review.name: NO ONE ON EARTH IS THIS FUNNY!!!!
review.reviewBody: Eddie Izzard is undoubtedly the funniest man alive, maybe who has ever lived!!! He is a joy, he puts on a one man extravaganza. It is not just a stand-up routine. He talks to his audience, really converses with them. The way his thought process flows is incredible! You will laugh so hard- you will hurt! And then, you will fall madly in love with this nut! There is no way to get enough after you have been exposed to his humor... and there is no going back!
